Title: Vintage Series Masterpiece Cabinet Oak 230
Body:
The Vintage Series Masterpiece Cabinet 230 in Oak is a premium quality cabinet designed for the connoisseur. The fine furniture cabinet is superbly constructed in oak and can hold up to 186 bottles of wine. The two column universal racking can accommodate many champagne bottles as well as standard bottles. An array of options are available, including various door styles with or without UV resistant windows, side moldings, locks, lights and casters. [Breezaire digital cooling](/collections/breezaire-cooling-units) is standard on the Vintage Series Masterpiece Cabinet Oakwood 230 and provides superior cooling and monitoring capabilities. Upgraded cooling is available. Call our experts at 1-800-876-8789 with any questions about customizations.

Product Includes:

*   Real Glass Windows
*   Furniture Finish (Red Oak)
*   Lock & Lights
*   Side Molding
*   Top Vent

Title: Vintage Series Premiere Cru 220
Body:
The Premiere Cru Wine Cellars are crafted with careful attention to detail. They have trim, elegant lines and a sophisticated look.

They are superbly constructed with California red oak on the exterior and the interiors are fitted with all heart redwood racking. Breezaire Digital Cooling Systems with light up temperature display is standard to maintain optimum wine storage conditions.

Choose from an array of door styles and options including furniture finishes, lock, interior light and casters.

Title: Vintage Series Wine Room 900
Body: Having your very own walk-in cellar has never been easier. The Vintage Series Wine Rooms are affordable, attractive and built to last. These easy-to-assemble walk-in wine rooms are made from reinforced panels that prevent warping. The panels have a beautiful oak exterior and mahogany interior. All-heart redwood racking and a quality Breezaire cooling unit complete the environment, ensuring optimum wine storage temperature while bottles are securely cradled in individual racks, stored "bulk style" or in full cases. Add a furniture stain and window door for a truly striking finish.
Collections: Walk In Wine Rooms,Vintage Series Wine Rooms

Title: Vintage Series Galaxy 340
Body: The Vintage Series Galaxy 340 is an attractive contemporary cabinet constructed from high quality materials for reliability and durability for the life of your wine. The Vintage Series Galaxy 340 wine cellar has heavy-duty insulation to maintain ideal temperatures despite fluctuating conditions outside the cabinet. The door and sides of the Vintage Series Galaxy 340 wine storage cabinet are double insulated solid mahogany to keep the full power of the Breezaire cooling system inside the cabinet where it belongs. Universal racking has space for Champagne and magnum sized bottles as well as standard bottles. Grapevine handles and a rich walnut finish complete the attractive appearance of the Vintage Series Galaxy 340 wine cabinet. A larger[Vintage Series Galaxy 540](/collections/vintage-series/vintage-series-galaxy-540) wine cabinet is also available.

Title: Legacy Wine Credenza 3-Door Single
Body: The Legacy series is a new line of wine storage credenzas from Vintage Series. The Vintage Series Legacy Wine Credenza 3-door, single bottle depth holds approximately 120 bottles on all redwood racking. The racking system of the Legacy Wine Credenza is designed to hold bottles of all sizes and shapes. Legacy wine credenzas feature a solid cherry hardwood door with a choice of trim options, a beautiful light cherry stain and fine furniture finish. All glass is UV resistant to protect the contents of your Legacy wine credenza. The cooling system is a new dark charcoal [Breezaire](#) cabinet cooling system with a 5 year warranty and a digital display for perfect temperature control. The Vintage Series Legacy Wine Credenza is available in 3 or 4 door sizes and single or double depths.

Title: Vintage Series Credenza 2 Door Single
Body:
The Vintage Series 2 door single-deep credenza is a beautifully crafted console style furniture piece with a [Breezaire](#) cooling unit to keep your wine at the ideal temperature for aging. Digital controls ensure accurate temperature management and thermopane windows keep sunlight out. The interior of the Vintage Series Credenza is filled with all heart redwood racking to hold all your bottles securely. The Vintage Series 2 door single-deep credenza is available in Oak or Cherry, each with a choice of several finishes. Several door styles are also available, along with raised molding upgrades. The Vintage Series 2 door single-deep credenza holds approximately 82 bottles.

[Vintage Series Credenzas](/collections/vintage-series-credenzas) are available in 2, 3 or 4 door styles and single- or double-bottle depths. The [Vintage Series 2-door Double Deep Credenza is available here](/collections/vintage-series-credenzas/vintage-series-credenza-2-door-double).
